    eng: At regular intervals, a wave of bubbles appears from off-screen, heading
      toward the player, and sweeps across the screen.
    jp: 
    cn: 
  - string_id: 44042
    category: active_skill
    context: "\uC2A4\uD0AC \uD6A8\uACFC \uC11C\uC220"
    kr: "\uC801\uC774 \uAC15\uD574\uC9C0\uACE0 \uACBD\uD5D8\uCE58\uAC00 \uC99D\uAC00\uB429\uB2C8\uB2E4."
    eng: Enemies become stronger and you gain more experience points.
    jp: 
    cn: 
  - string_id: 44043
